org.mitre.provenance.dag

Class PathCatalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap<String,List<String>>
        • org.mitre.provenance.dag.PathCatalog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,List<String>>

    public class PathCatalog
extends HashMap<String,List<String>>
    A catalog of paths through a DAG. This is a map of keys to paths; keys correspond to the two OIDs of nodes in the graph, values correspond to a list of OIDs in sequence describing a path through the graph to reach from one OID to the other.
    Author:
    dmallen
